209
00:09:44,876 --> 00:09:46,252
HMM?

210
00:09:46,252 --> 00:09:50,590
HOW DID YOU EVER END UP
BECOMING THIS SOMA PERIES?

211
00:09:50,590 --> 00:09:52,258
THEY PROBABLY...

212
00:09:52,258 --> 00:09:55,053
IMPLANTED
ANOTHER PERSONALITY,

213
00:09:55,053 --> 00:09:56,721
IN ORDER TO RESTORE
THE FIVE SENSES

214
00:09:56,721 --> 00:09:58,431
THAT I'D LOST.

215
00:09:58,431 --> 00:10:00,767
THEN THE SUPERHUMAN INSTITUTE
MUST HAVE SENT ME

216
00:10:00,767 --> 00:10:02,769
TO THE MILITARY TO SERVE
AS A SUPER SOLDIER

217
00:10:02,769 --> 00:10:05,480
