THEY WOULDN'T BE CLOSED DOWN.

218
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:07,190
HOW TERRIBLE FOR YOU.

219
00:10:07,190 --> 00:10:07,649
YES.

220
00:10:07,649 --> 00:10:08,900
YES.
HMM?

221
