239
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,911
MY FRIENDS AND I WERE ABLE TO
STEAL A TRANSPORT SHIP

240
00:11:01,911 --> 00:11:04,372
AND ESCAPE THE COLONY.

241
00:11:04,372 --> 00:11:08,209
BUT WE HAD NO PLACE TO GO.

242
00:11:08,209 --> 00:11:10,545
